text: Wil Yamamoto (born 11 January 1974) is a former cyclist from Guam. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Guamanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Guam Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
